* structured_text_bidi_override (StructuredTextParser): Default: 0
* structured_text_bidi_override_options (Array): Default: []
* text (String): Default: ""
* text_direction (Direction): Default: 0
* uppercase (bool): Default: false
* vertical_alignment (VerticalAlignment): Default: 1
* width (float): Default: 500.0
